SV_NAME: Surrey-Newton Urgent and Primary Care Centre
SV_DESCRIPTION: Provides team-based care for non-emergency health concerns to individuals in the Surrey-Newton area. Offers same-day care for concerns such as minor injuries, sprains and strains, less serious child illness and injury, infections, and cuts, wounds or skin conditions. Call before going to the clinic to confirm current availability and hours. Please call the clinic before faxing confidential patient information. ECG, IV Therapy and medical imaging such as x-ray services, are not offered at this location. For COVID-19 testing information, visit the BC Centre for Disease Control (BCCDC) testing page to find a collection centre near you.

Patients pre-registered at the clinic for primary care services should call to book an appointment.
